data.description: “Beautiful Townhome!” This well maintained, 2 bed, 1.5 bath townhome is ready for you to move right in! It has everything you need including the refrigerator! All updates include new sliding double doors to the patio, hvac is 5 years old, water heater is 2 years old, some new windows (all were replaced in 2014), new surround shower in master bath, and some new fixtures. It has laminate floors, lots of closets, tile backsplash, and large side yard with patio. This lovely unit will not last long!
